    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
        <li><a href="/hikes">My Hikes</a></li>
        <li><a href="/recommendations">Recommendations</a></li>

      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <h1 class="title" style="background-color: #2255bb;">Recommendations</h1>
  <main>
    <p style="font-size: 1.5rem;">Welcome to the recommendations page! This page contains some recommendations from the
      creators of hikes they have
      been on. Click to to get more information about each hike. Once you've been on one, make sure to update your
      tracker!</p>
